keyFeatures: <body><ul><li><b>Make quick work of your work</b><br />Get things done - all on one device. Take notes, collaborate and work seamlessly between apps. From pie charts to pie recipes, Tablet is designed for all kinds of productivity.</li><li><b>Take notes and collaborate</b><br />The A14 Bionic chip delivers power and performance for any activity. Edit a 4K video in iMovie, plan a globe-trotting vacation with friends or play a graphics-intensive game. With all-day battery life, you can do it all without skipping a beat.</li><li><b>Create to your heart's content</b><br />Express yourself, draw and brainstorm on a flexible creative powerhouse. The stunning 10.9" Liquid Retina display makes an incredible canvas.</li><li><b>High-quality audio</b><br />Record and refine from anywhere with high-quality built-in mics and landscape stereo speakers. Start a podcast, compose a beat, score a film - your creative projects sound fantastic.</li><li><b>Get in touch - stay in frame</b><br />With the landscape 12MP ultra-wide front camera, you'll be perfectly in frame whether you're on a FaceTime call, attending a video conference or recording a selfie. And with Center Stage, the camera automatically adjusts to keep you centered in the shot.</li><li><b>Super-fast connections</b><br />Download files, play games online and stream movies with Wi-Fi 6.</li><li><b>Outstanding display</b><br />Dive into your favorite shows, apps and games on the beautiful 10.9" Liquid Retina display. And with True Tone technology, it's comfortable to view in any light.</li></ul></body>
